@startuml SC-51-Export-RGPD-AdminSecretariat
!theme plain
title Diagramme de Collaboration - Export Données RGPD

object AdminSecretariat
object "Interface Web" as InterfaceWeb
object "Data Export Service" as ExportService
object "Base Données" as BaseDonnees
object "Encryption Service" as EncryptService
object "Storage Service (S3)" as StorageService
object "Email Service" as EmailService
object "Job Queue (BullMQ)" as JobQueue
object "Notification Service" as NotifService

AdminSecretariat --> InterfaceWeb : 1: accede(/dashboard/data-export)
InterfaceWeb --> AdminSecretariat : 2: affiche(options_export)

AdminSecretariat --> InterfaceWeb : 3: selectScope(Clients, Employes, Fiches, Period)
AdminSecretariat --> InterfaceWeb : 4: selectFormat(CSV/JSON/XML)
AdminSecretariat --> InterfaceWeb : 5: selectInclusions(Documents, AuditLogs)

AdminSecretariat --> InterfaceWeb : 6: clique(Generer export)
InterfaceWeb --> AdminSecretariat : 7: affiche(Preparation en cours...)

InterfaceWeb --> JobQueue : 8: enqueue(EXPORT_DATA_JOB)
JobQueue --> InterfaceWeb : 9: jobId_returned

JobQueue --> ExportService : 10: lance(asynchrone)
ExportService --> BaseDonnees : 11: SELECT ALL\nWHERE secretariatId = ?
BaseDonnees --> ExportService : 12: retourneData_complet

ExportService --> ExportService : 13: formate(CSV/JSON/XML)\net valide

ExportService --> EncryptService : 14: chiffre(AES-256)
EncryptService --> EncryptService : 15: genere(password_aleatoire)
EncryptService --> ExportService : 16: retourneArchive_chiffre

ExportService --> StorageService : 17: stocke(S3, expiration=7j)
StorageService --> ExportService : 18: retourneLinkSecurise

ExportService --> JobQueue : 19: marque(COMPLETED)
JobQueue --> ExportService : 20: jobStatus_updated

ExportService --> EmailService : 21: envoieEmail(lien_securise)
EmailService --> EmailService : 22: genere(email_avec_lien)
EmailService --> AdminSecretariat : 23: reçoitEmail

AdminSecretariat --> StorageService : 24: clique(lien_email)
StorageService --> AdminSecretariat : 25: telecharge(fichier.zip)

ExportService --> BaseDonnees : 26: INSERT log audit\n(DATA_EXPORT_COMPLETED)

note right of ExportService
Protections RGPD:
- Chiffrement AES-256
- Mot de passe séparé
- Expiration 7 jours
- Audit trail complet
- Format lisible (CSV/JSON/XML)
end note

AdminSecretariat --> InterfaceWeb : 27a: clique(Demander suppression)
InterfaceWeb --> AdminSecretariat : 27b: affiche(modal_confirmation)

AdminSecretariat --> InterfaceWeb : 28: confirme(DELETE)
InterfaceWeb --> ExportService : 29: submitDeletionRequest(secretariatId)

ExportService --> BaseDonnees : 30: SELECT secretariat_id

ExportService --> BaseDonnees : 31: planifie(soft_delete, +30j)
BaseDonnees --> ExportService : 31.1: ok

ExportService --> EmailService : 32: envoieEmail(confirmation)
EmailService --> AdminSecretariat : 33: reçoitEmail_confirmation

ExportService --> BaseDonnees : 34: INSERT log audit\n(DELETION_REQUESTED)

AdminSecretariat --> InterfaceWeb : 35a: clique(Annuler suppression)
InterfaceWeb --> ExportService : 35b: submitCancellation
ExportService --> BaseDonnees : 36: UPDATE(deletion = NULL)
ExportService --> EmailService : 37: envoieEmail(annulee)
EmailService --> AdminSecretariat : 38: confirmation_reçue

note right of BaseDonnees
Cycle de suppression:
- J0: Demande suppression
- J0 à J30: Droit rétractation
- J30: Soft-delete automatique
- Données marquées deleted_at
- Accès révoqué aux sessions
end note

@enduml
